subtests.name: touch coalesced events attributes in pointerevents
touch pointercancel should not have any coalesced events
touch pointerover should not have any coalesced events
touch pointerenter should not have any coalesced events
touch pointerdown should not have any coalesced events
touch pointermove should have >2 coalesced events as main thread is busy.
touch pointermove coalesced events should all be marked as trusted.
touch time stamps of coalesced events must be ascending.
touch pointermove coalesced events should all bubbles and cancelable as false.
touch pointerup should not have any coalesced events
touch pointerout should not have any coalesced events
touch pointerleave should not have any coalesced events
